                <mxCell id="p1_legend" value="What this page shows:  the OUTER ring of the hexagon — how the system is entered.&#xa;Each pipeline is the ONLY place callers compose work; APIs never reach past pipelines.&#xa;Dashed = new endpoint to be added (replaces in-UI Streamlit imports of pipeline code)." style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=11;fontColor=#23445d;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#23445d;rounded=1;spacingLeft=12;" parent="1" vertex="1">
