                <mxCell id="p5_src_h" value="TODAY  —  services/" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=14;fontStyle=1;fillColor=#23445d;fontColor=#ffffff;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="170" width="460" height="32" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p5_src_t" value="transformer_model.py  (2740 LOC)&#xa;&#xa;5 concerns mixed in one file:&#xa;• ML architecture (PositionalEncoding, ExpertActionTransformer)&#xa;• Feature scaler (PerFeatureScaler, _RunningFeatureStats)&#xa;• Streaming dataset (TelemetryActionDataset)&#xa;• Training loop (ExpertActionTrainer — AMP, checkpoints)&#xa;• Async entry function (prepare_and_train_coach_…)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1f6091;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="210" width="460" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p5_src_i" value="imitate_expert_learning_service.py  (1121 LOC)&#xa;&#xa;3 concerns:&#xa;• Domain types (ExpertFeatureCatalog, SegmentImprovementConfig,&#xa;  SegmentImprovementSummary, ExpertModelTrainingConfig)&#xa;• ML model (TrackExpertModel, ExpertPositionLearner +&#xa;  serialize / deserialize helpers)&#xa;• Orchestrator service (ExpertImitateLearningService.train_ai_model)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#2d5e2d;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="380" width="460" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p5_src_s" value="segment_classifier_service.py  (996 LOC)&#xa;&#xa;5 concerns:&#xa;• ML model (FocalLoss, CNN1DModel — small, ~50 lines)&#xa;• Dataset + derived features (StreamingSegmentDataset)&#xa;• Model + scaler I/O (torch.save, joblib.dump/load)&#xa;• Training pipeline (prepare_training_data, train_model)&#xa;• Inference (load_model, predict_segment, scan_session)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#5d3b6f;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="550" width="460" height="160" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p5_src_tg" value="tire_grip_analysis_service.py  (186 LOC)  ★ NOT ML&#xa;&#xa;Physics formula. No fit / predict / torch.&#xa;&#xa;2 concerns:&#xa;• Domain types (TireGripFeatureCatalog, SlipEnvelopeConfig)&#xa;• Stateless feature engineering (extract_tire_grip_features,&#xa;  friction-circle math)&#xa;&#xa;The no-op train stubs at lines 102–134 should be deleted." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#b35900;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="720" width="460" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="p5_src_fd" value="full_dataset_ml_service.py  (1209 LOC)&#xa;&#xa;Pure orchestrator. NO model code lives here.&#xa;&#xa;3 concerns:&#xa;• Training orchestration (prepare_training_data,&#xa;  run_transformer_guidance_training, process_lap_sessions_efficiently)&#xa;• Inference (predict_expert_actions)&#xa;• Direct module imports of the 4 sibling services + LLM + backend&#xa;  ⚠ these should become injected dependencies, not imports" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#7a2e2c;strokeWidth=3;fontSize=11;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="900" width="460" height="180" as="geometry"/>
